I"Z<p><a href="https://www.brendanmartin.com/">Brendan</a> has succinctly summed up what we do in three simple steps that will improve your life:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Be more interested</li>
  <li>Give more plusses</li>
  <li>Enjoy the game</li>
</ol>

<p>I covered the first point in <a href="https://isene.org/2018/09/Podcast-EasilyHurt.html">an earlier blog post</a>. It is also covered in our OnePageBook, “<a href="https://isene.org/onepagebooks/#1pb-2-mental-training---the-core">Mental training - The core</a>”.</p>

<p>The second point is covered <strong><a href="https://isene.org/2018/11/Podcast-Impress.html">in several</a></strong> <a href="https://isene.org/2018/10/Podcast-HelpOthers.html">earlier</a> <strong><a href="https://isene.org/2018/12/Podcast-MeaningOfLife.html">posts</a></strong>.</p>

<p>And the third point was the subject of <a href="https://isene.org/2019/07/Enjoy.html">a post this summer</a>.</p>

<p>The elegance of summing it all up in just three simple points is the genius of Brendan.</p>

<p>The inspiration moved me to create a simple online presentation: “<a href="https://isene.github.io/">How to improve your life</a>”</p>

